freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Extreme fatigue & joint aches for 2 days. It has lessened as the week has gone on.  Began 3/14/21.  I had to take the am of 3/16/21 off to rest & stretch (things I normally do, but did even more and hot baths with Epsom salt.) No abnormal activity.

freetext.SYSTEMIC_REACTION_OTHER: Injection site is warm.  Only thing so far!
